entry.title: CMU-SAFARI/RowPress
entry.summary: Source code & scripts for experimental characterization and real-system demonstration of RowPress, a widespread read disturbance phenomenon in DRAM that is different from RowHammer. Described in our ISCA'23 paper by Luo et al. at https://people.inf.ethz.ch/omutlu/pub/RowPress_isca23.pdf
